      | o=\in
      | r=S
      | c=Definition of [[Definition:Closed Algebraic Structure|closed algebraic structure]]
}}
{{eqn | ll=\implies
      | l=\left({x_1 \circ y_1}\right)
      | o=\mathcal R
      | r=\left({x_2 \circ y_2}\right)
      | c=Definition of [[Definition:Trivial Relation|Trivial Relation]]
